{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.002,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut ainsi adress\u00e9e \u00e0 J\u00e9hu, fils de Hanani, contre Baescha:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.2","name":"1 Rois 16:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.34","name":"1 Rois 15:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Je t\u2019ai \u00e9lev\u00e9 de la poussi\u00e8re, et je t\u2019ai \u00e9tabli chef de mon peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; mais parce que tu as march\u00e9 dans la voie de J\u00e9roboam, et que tu as fait p\u00e9cher mon peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, pour m\u2019irriter par leurs p\u00e9ch\u00e9s,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.3","name":"1 Rois 16:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.1","name":"1 Rois 16:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>voici, je vais balayer Baescha et sa maison, et je rendrai ta maison semblable \u00e0 la maison de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.4","name":"1 Rois 16:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.2","name":"1 Rois 16:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Celui de la maison de Baescha qui mourra dans la ville sera mang\u00e9 par les chiens, et celui des siens qui mourra dans les champs sera mang\u00e9 par les oiseaux du ciel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.5","name":"1 Rois 16:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.3","name":"1 Rois 16:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Baescha, ce qu\u2019il a fait, et ses exploits, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.6","name":"1 Rois 16:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.4","name":"1 Rois 16:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Baescha se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et il fut enterr\u00e9 \u00e0 Thirtsa. Et \u00c9la, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.7","name":"1 Rois 16:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.5","name":"1 Rois 16:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel s\u2019\u00e9tait manifest\u00e9e par le proph\u00e8te J\u00e9hu, fils de Hanani, contre Baescha et contre sa maison, soit \u00e0 cause de tout le mal qu\u2019il avait fait sous les yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en l\u2019irritant par l\u2019\u0153uvre de ses mains et en devenant semblable \u00e0 la maison de J\u00e9roboam, soit parce qu\u2019il avait frapp\u00e9 la maison de J\u00e9roboam.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.8","name":"1 Rois 16:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.6","name":"1 Rois 16:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-14: cf. 1 R 15:25-30. Ex 20:5. Ps 109:14. (Ps 119:89. \u00c9s 40:8.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>La vingt-sixi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Asa, roi de Juda, \u00c9la, fils de Baescha, r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 Thirtsa. Il r\u00e9gna deux ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.9","name":"1 Rois 16:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.7","name":"1 Rois 16:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Son serviteur Zimri, chef de la moiti\u00e9 des chars, conspira contre lui. \u00c9la \u00e9tait \u00e0 Thirtsa, buvant et s\u2019enivrant dans la maison d\u2019Artsa, chef de la maison du roi \u00e0 Thirtsa.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.10","name":"1 Rois 16:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.8","name":"1 Rois 16:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Zimri entra, le frappa et le tua, la vingt-septi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Asa, roi de Juda, et il r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.11","name":"1 Rois 16:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.9","name":"1 Rois 16:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019il fut roi et qu\u2019il fut assis sur son tr\u00f4ne, il frappa toute la maison de Baescha, il ne laissa \u00e9chapper personne qui lui appart\u00eent, ni parent ni ami.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.12","name":"1 Rois 16:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.10","name":"1 Rois 16:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Zimri d\u00e9truisit toute la maison de Baescha, selon la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait dite contre Baescha par J\u00e9hu, le proph\u00e8te,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.13","name":"1 Rois 16:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.11","name":"1 Rois 16:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>\u00e0 cause de tous les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que Baescha et \u00c9la, son fils, avaient commis et qu\u2019ils avaient fait commettre \u00e0 Isra\u00ebl, irritant par leurs idoles l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.14","name":"1 Rois 16:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.12","name":"1 Rois 16:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Le reste des actions d\u2019\u00c9la, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.15","name":"1 Rois 16:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.13","name":"1 Rois 16:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-22: cf. 2 R 15:8-15. (J\u00e9 17:11. Job 8:13-19.) Job 34:23-25.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>La vingt-septi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Asa, roi de Juda, Zimri r\u00e9gna sept jours \u00e0 Thirtsa. Le peuple campait contre Guibbethon, qui appartenait aux Philistins.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.16","name":"1 Rois 16:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.14","name":"1 Rois 16:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Et le peuple qui campait apprit cette nouvelle: Zimri a conspir\u00e9, et m\u00eame il a tu\u00e9 le roi! Et ce jour-l\u00e0, tout Isra\u00ebl \u00e9tablit dans le camp pour roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl Omri, chef de l\u2019arm\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.17","name":"1 Rois 16:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.15","name":"1 Rois 16:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Omri et tout Isra\u00ebl avec lui partirent de Guibbethon, et ils assi\u00e9g\u00e8rent Thirtsa.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.18","name":"1 Rois 16:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.16","name":"1 Rois 16:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Zimri, voyant que la ville \u00e9tait prise, se retira dans le palais de la maison du roi, et br\u00fbla sur lui la maison du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.19","name":"1 Rois 16:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.17","name":"1 Rois 16:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>C\u2019est ainsi qu\u2019il mourut, \u00e0 cause des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s qu\u2019il avait commis en faisant ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en marchant dans la voie de J\u00e9roboam, et en se livrant aux p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que J\u00e9roboam avait commis pour faire p\u00e9cher Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.20","name":"1 Rois 16:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.18","name":"1 Rois 16:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Zimri, et la conspiration qu\u2019il forma, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.21","name":"1 Rois 16:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.19","name":"1 Rois 16:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Alors le peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl se divisa en deux partis: une moiti\u00e9 du peuple voulait faire roi Thibni, fils de Guinath, et l\u2019autre moiti\u00e9 \u00e9tait pour Omri.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.22","name":"1 Rois 16:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.20","name":"1 Rois 16:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Ceux qui suivaient Omri l\u2019emport\u00e8rent sur ceux qui suivaient Thibni, fils de Guinath. Thibni mourut, et Omri r\u00e9gna.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.23","name":"1 Rois 16:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.21","name":"1 Rois 16:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.024,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 23-28: cf. Mi 6:16. 2 Ti 3:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>La trente et uni\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Asa, roi de Juda, Omri r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl. Il r\u00e9gna douze ans. Apr\u00e8s avoir r\u00e9gn\u00e9 six ans \u00e0 Thirtsa,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.24","name":"1 Rois 16:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.22","name":"1 Rois 16:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>il acheta de Sch\u00e9mer la montagne de Samarie pour deux talents d\u2019argent; il b\u00e2tit sur la montagne, et il donna \u00e0 la ville qu\u2019il b\u00e2tit le nom de Samarie, d\u2019apr\u00e8s le nom de Sch\u00e9mer, seigneur de la montagne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.25","name":"1 Rois 16:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.23","name":"1 Rois 16:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Omri fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il agit plus mal que tous ceux qui avaient \u00e9t\u00e9 avant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.26","name":"1 Rois 16:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.24","name":"1 Rois 16:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Il marcha dans toute la voie de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, et se livra aux p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que J\u00e9roboam avait fait commettre \u00e0 Isra\u00ebl, irritant par leurs idoles l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.27","name":"1 Rois 16:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.25","name":"1 Rois 16:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Le reste des actions d\u2019Omri, ce qu\u2019il a fait, et ses exploits, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.28","name":"1 Rois 16:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.26","name":"1 Rois 16:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Omri se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et il fut enterr\u00e9 \u00e0 Samarie. Et Achab, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.29","name":"1 Rois 16:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.27","name":"1 Rois 16:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.030,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Achab, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. \u2014 Son mariage avec J\u00e9zabel, fille du roi des Sidoniens<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 29-34: cf. 1 R 18:1-18; 21. Ap 2:20-23.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Achab, fils d\u2019Omri, r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl, la trente-huiti\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Asa, roi de Juda. Achab, fils d\u2019Omri, r\u00e9gna vingt-deux ans sur Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 Samarie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.30","name":"1 Rois 16:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.28","name":"1 Rois 16:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Achab, fils d\u2019Omri, fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, plus que tous ceux qui avaient \u00e9t\u00e9 avant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.31","name":"1 Rois 16:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.29","name":"1 Rois 16:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Et comme si c\u2019e\u00fbt \u00e9t\u00e9 pour lui peu de chose de se livrer aux p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, il prit pour femme J\u00e9zabel, fille d\u2019Ethbaal, roi des Sidoniens, et il alla servir Baal et se prosterner devant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.32","name":"1 Rois 16:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.30","name":"1 Rois 16:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.32","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:32","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Il \u00e9leva un autel \u00e0 Baal dans la maison de Baal qu\u2019il b\u00e2tit \u00e0 Samarie,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.33","name":"1 Rois 16:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.31","name":"1 Rois 16:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.33","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:33","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>et il fit une idole d\u2019Astart\u00e9. Achab fit plus encore que tous les rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl qui avaient \u00e9t\u00e9 avant lui, pour irriter l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.34","name":"1 Rois 16:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.32","name":"1 Rois 16:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.34","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 16:34","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.017.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.16.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>De son temps, Hiel de B\u00e9thel b\u00e2tit J\u00e9richo; il en jeta les fondements au prix d\u2019Abiram, son premier-n\u00e9, et il en posa les portes au prix de Segub, son plus jeune fils, selon la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait dite par Josu\u00e9, fils de Nun.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16","name":"1 Rois 16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.17.1","name":"1 Rois 17:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.17.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.33","name":"1 Rois 16:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb4664ba8.72632927');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb4664ba8.72632927\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb4664ba8.72632927","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb4664ba8.72632927'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb4664ba8.72632927\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}